Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo appears at the base of\nthe sacred mountain, Mt. Hakurei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so does Ginkotsu,\neven more powerful than before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Suikotsu of the Band of Seven,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the one with two hearts,\nhas also awakened!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:21.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairytale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:24.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't he part of\nthe Band of Seven?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I... I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}\NDr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\nWhat are you doing, Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}\nHe's finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.\NBad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die...{\i0}\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:03:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die...{\i0}\NIron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Suikotsu of the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That do-good physician...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,held me back for\nso long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's an entirely different\nperson from a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Suikotsu has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,two hearts inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's called split personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another personality hidden in the\nsubconscious has emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One thing I do know... you belong\nto the Band of Seven, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been wanting\nto fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll get your wish now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:48.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too scared to fight\nwithout a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Plan to fight me\nwith those claws?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:58.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see you try,\nyou deceitful bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch what you say, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-reaver, Soul-stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll turn you into mincemeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your moves are too showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Close-quarters combat is\nfought like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you keep backing away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'll never be able to\nmince me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get too cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:29.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:43.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please return to\nyour old self!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy...\NWhat's happening to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That Suikotsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He hasn't completely awakened yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, Ginkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha can't reach her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you can't use your\NWind Tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not the time\nto say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you stay close to Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And open up the way with\nyour Hiraikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! You can go, after\nyou beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... she's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! She wasn't the real target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:13.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! I'm not too keen\non this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we kill the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there will be no one left\nto distract Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then he'll be able to suppress\nthat troublesome doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NIt'll be real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please... Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Suikotsu... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suikotsu still has\nfeelings of uncertainty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we kill the kids...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}his heart may burst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The barrier of Mt. Hakurei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get 'em all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems we can't linger around here\nany longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come, Suikotsu!\NRetreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You ain't getting' away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:53.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How {\i1}irritating....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:11:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please get up, Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:10.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have the souls of the dead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}left her body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:32.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo's Soul Collectors...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can't get near her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to take Kikyo\nover there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Otherwise, she probably\ncan't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Should I be the one\nto carry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only Inuyasha can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it my imagination, or\nare things a bit tense here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not your imagination, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to see them\nlike this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it can't be helped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me, does Inuyasha still\nhave feelings for Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez, you have to admire\NKagome's generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't say such\nthings right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I sound scary to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Soul Collectors could not\nget near the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:08.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, the Band of Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:18.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The men who possess those\ndefiled Sacred Jewel {\i1}shards....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They took Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard around\NSuikotsu's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The clear glow turned cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And then... he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo... what're you trying to say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This land is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It does not allow anyone with a\ndemonic aura to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is because Mt. Hakurei is purifying\nthe air in the surrounding areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is a sacred mountain which absolves\nand cleanses criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That man known as Suikotsu was\nable to live here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because deep inside, he had\na pure heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But his other personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Suikotsu who belonged to\nthe Band of Seven surfaced,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so he wasn't able\nto stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rest of the gang\nstopped fighting and left
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because of this mountain\nknown as Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pure is impure.\NImpure is pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good is bad.\NBad is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:59.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To live is to die.\NTo die is to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei is too pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mt. Hakurei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we do, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go.\NI'm curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to stay close to\nthose children for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:40.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I wish to,\NI cannot go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Soul Collectors are being repelled\nfrom this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It took all I had to stand\nat the base of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, do you still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Why's Kagome riding Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, because she doesn't\nwant to be carried by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'd I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you didn't do a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:06.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the mood between you and\NKikyo is too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women are very sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:14.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is hurt because she thinks\nthat you still have feelings for Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let her be for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Kagome has cooled down,\nyou can get on her good side again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:27.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wasn't listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer me, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have something to say,\nlet's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:00.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, this is no time to argue.\NYou understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I mentioned it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That I'll stay beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that there's a bond between\nyou and Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I can't tell you to\nforget Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:30.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's what I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'm not going to worry\nabout last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to pick\na fight with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:49.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can't you just\nleave me alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm trying so hard\nto endure this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You're angry, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:08.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid, stupid, stupid, stupid!\NSit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I told him\nto let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha looks so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:21.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:32.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Renkotsu!\NWhere're we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:38.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:41.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's come for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, let's go meet\nthe Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Band of Seven will\nbe at full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The strongest of the specters, Bankotsu,\nhas rejoined the Band of Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're hell-bent on revenge\nand begin an assault of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those bastards in that castle\nbeheaded us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.13,0:24:00.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel stronger than\nbefore I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me they're also\nafter Koga's Sacred Jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha: "Enter Bankotsu,\nthe Leader of the Band of Seven"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wash your necks and wait to die!
